status.description: A resolution has been taken, and it is awaiting verification by reporter. From here issues are either reopened, or are closed.

comments.comment:
I have verified that AS7-5688 is is fixed by the resolved issue ISPN-2845 for AS 7.1.1. Here is what I did to verify:

  • build Infinispan 5.2.3-SNAPSHOT which contains the fix
  • checkout AS 7.1.1.Final
  • modify the top-level pom to use the new Infinispan version
  • build the project
  • de-ignore org.jboss.as.test.clustering.cluster.web.passivation. {AttributeBasedSessionPassivationTestCase, SessionBasedSessionPassivationTestCase}
  • run the clustering testsuite
    ./integration-tests.sh clean install -Dts.clust -Dts.noSmoke
    Tests pass. Will check for 7.1.3.
Tried the same replacement for 7.1.3 but there were many more integration issues to deal with.

Tried the same replacement for 7.2.0.Alpha1 and the tests passed without incident. Not sure of this version of Infinispan will make it into 7.2.0.Final. If yes, then this issue can probably be closed.
